# How to clone a VM?

You can clone a VM by following the steps below:

- Login to client portal from https://portal.serverpoint.com/cgi-bin/gen4cp/engine/login.cgi
- Click "Manage your Vms" 
- Click "Settings of the VM" you need
- Click "Actions" and click "Save VM as template / One-time backup"
- Name the snapshot template. You can save this VM as a reusable snapshot template. 
- Once the snapshot is ready, proceed to deploy a new VM. (Create VM)
- Select the newly created template from  drop down box below "choose one of your existing templates" while selecting OS.
